| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4513 — Recovery Inhibition (beast)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1b9a10a4-c9fc-5438-b4b8-df87bbd9909e"
